defs.name: ParserErrorKind
defs.value:
pub enum ParserErrorKind {
    ExpectedFunIdent,
    ExpectedReturnType,
    ExpectedFunBody,
    ExpectedImportLocation,
    ExpectedAsAlias,
    ExpectedImportIdent,
    ExpectedVarIdent,
    ExpectedValIdent,
    ExpectedAssignment,
    ExpectedOperator,
    ExpectedIfCondition,
    ExpectedIfThenBody,
    ExpectedIfElseBody,
    ExpectedWhileBody,
    ExpectedIdent,
    ExpectedType,
    ExpectedTip,
    ExpectedExpressionStatement,
    ExpectedBlockStmtStart,
    ExpectedBlockStmtEnd,
    ExpectedUnaryOperator,
    ExpectedBinaryOperator,
    ExpectedPrimaryExpression,
    ExpectedProgramStmt,
    ExpectedExpression,
    ExpectedOperand,
    ExpectedKeyword(Keyword),
    ExpectedToken(Token),
    ExpectedTokens(Vec<Token>),
    ExpectedTokenType(String),
    UnexpectedEOF,
    MissingDelimiter,
}
